	   INV()   -	*   *	 *  -  -  M=N
	   TRANS() *	*   *	 *  -  -  M=N

Furthermore there are operators or functions which operate in between two 
varable classes: e.g.

a%=INT(b), c=DET(d()), s=SMUL(a(),b()), a()=NULL(2,4,5), ...

